1.title: Episode #10.1
1.plot: Jojo heads to the Panhandle of Florida to manage his beach house rental and get some R&R.

2.title: Episode #10.2
2.plot: Jojo meets up with Destin's BEST Realtor, Andrea Farrell, to discuss the local vacation rental market.

3.title: Episode #10.3
3.plot: Jojo meets up with Panhandle Developer, Camilo Giraldo, to tour a beautiful new construction at Destin Pointe.

4.title: We Got the House!/Nick Arrives
4.plot: Jojo and Maricel decide whether or not to invest in a new vacation rental property and Nick arrives from California.

5.title: Nick's Tasks
5.plot: Jojo assigns Nick a list of tasks to complete at the new property.

6.title: Emerald Grande
6.plot: Jojo is back with Camilo Giraldo for a tour of Emerald Grande and one of the property's premier penthouses.

7.title: Episode #10.7
7.plot: Jojo and Camilo visit Legendary Marina and get a special tour of Lulu's Restaurant while repairs continue on the new property.

8.title: Episode #10.8
8.plot: Maricel and Crystal visit the town of Seaside and its famous Farmer's Market while Nick does some repairs back at the house.

9.title: Episode #10.9
9.plot: Nick meets one of his idols, Dr. Lisa Clark of Clark Family Medicine and author of Lighten Up, America: Odds and Not-So-Fat Ends of Weight Management.

10.title: Episode #10.10
10.plot: Jojo is back with Andrea Farrell to tour one of Destin's most luxurious vacation rentals.

11.title: Episode #10.11
11.plot: Jojo meets with local Developer James Lopez to discuss the Tech World.

12.title: Episode #10.12
12.plot: Jojo meets Daniel, the Lead Chef at Destin's popular Capriccio Cafe, to discuss his journey in coffee and crepes.

13.title: Episode #10.13
13.plot: Join us in this Season 11 RECAP.
